# Decisions log for yentl-hardening-pass
#
# Append-only audit trail. Worker appends one entry per run; watchdog appends one entry per audit.
#
# Worker entry format:
#   --- <ISO timestamp> ---
#   RUN #<N> (worker)
#   Goal terminated: <reason>
#   Attempted: <one-line summary>
#   Clauses progressed: <list of clause numbers>
#   Evaluator verdict: <verbatim if available, else "n/a">
#   Files changed: <list, or "none">
#   Git commits made: <short SHAs + subjects, or "none">
#   Cost (approx): $<X.XX>
#
# Watchdog entry format (clean audit):
#   [OK <ISO timestamp>] watchdog audit clean — runs: <N>, cost: $<X.XX>, status: <status>, clauses-met: <count>/14
#
# Watchdog entry format (issue found):
#   [ISSUE <ISO timestamp>] watchdog flagged check #<N>; see alerts.md
#
# Goal completion marker (worker):
#   [GOAL ACHIEVED <ISO timestamp>]
#
# Watchdog stop marker (critical issue):
#   [WATCHDOG STOP <ISO timestamp>]
#
# Watchdog confirmation of completion:
#   [WATCHDOG CONFIRMED COMPLETE <ISO timestamp>]
#
# Watchdog rejection of premature completion:
#   [WATCHDOG REJECTED COMPLETION <ISO timestamp>] worker claimed done but clause N not actually met
#
# ---

